{"title":"南方的爱","authors":["祁放"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":5,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祁　放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的爱是温馨的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫着金英子的花粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘溢着茶树的清香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清澈的小河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船做成一架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会摇晃的桥梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来寻找故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头的老樟树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却只对着我呆呆地望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也没想好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小时候奶奶哄我睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么总用她漏风的嘴巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许给我一只樟木箱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是南方的女儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是风把我带走的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，又象一朵雪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘回到这片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有雪花的土地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想做些什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕是一支水牛背上的小曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会把真诚的微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给每一个对我微笑的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的爱是深情的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不喜欢寂寞和悲伤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天从这里出发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进了千家万户的门窗……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}